title: Can't log in - Grey'd out Launch Button
body: I press the launch button and it just gets grey'd out, and I can't press anything else. Have re-downloaded the whole game already and still nothing.

replies.body:
Hey there,

At the launch screen please try typing the following and then attempt to launch the game.
>thereisnourflevel

I'm not sure if this still works but let me know if it helps.
I've tried that already and it does nothing at all, just makes the launch button spammable with no results. I need to wait like 20 minutes for it to get past the launch screen. Not even exaggerating.
Could you try running the launcher as admin, this can be done by right clicking on the launcher and selecting **Run as Administrator**.

> [{quoted}](name=SephirothSG,realm=OCE,application-id=ElA0rvVL,discussion-id=A89fEjRH,comment-id=000000000000,timestamp=2016-02-01T08:27:05.588+0000)
>
> Could you try running the launcher as admin, this can be done by right clicking on the launcher and selecting **Run as Administrator**.

That's the first thing I tried and nothing.
